original: Beijer, Erik, kyrkoherde, Bjärges, f. 22/6/09 i Gbg av mål :mäst. Hjalmar B. o. Anna Jo^hansson. G. 39 m. Anna-Stina Sundh. Barn: Göran f. 40, Gunilla 41, Birgitta 44. — Stud:ex. i Gbg 28, teol. fil. ex. 30, teol. kand. 36, stud. v. univ. i Berlin 36-37, prästv. f. Visby stift 38. V. kommin. i Visby 38, dom-kyrkoadj. där 39, kyrkoh. i Vänge,
translated: Beijer, Erik, clergyman, born on June 22, 1909 in Gothenburg, son of master Hjalmar B. and Anna Johansson. Married in 1939 to Anna-Stina Sundh. Children: Göran born in 1940, Gunilla in 1941 and Birgitta in 1944. He finished his studies with a high school diploma in Gothenburg in 1928, followed by a Bachelor of Theology in 1930 and a Master of Theology in 1936. He studied as a student at the University of Berlin from 1936-37 and was ordained as a priest for the Visby diocese in 1938. He worked as an assistant minister in Visby in 1938, a cathedral assistant in 1939 and as a vicar in Vänge.
